# What are the risks and benefits of a military campaign for Ukraine?

## Summary
The risks of a military campaign for Ukraine include the potential for escalation of the conflict with Russia, as well as the possibility of civilian casualties. The benefits of a military campaign could include the liberation of occupied territory and the restoration of Ukrainian sovereignty.

